name: Corinex Communications
overview: Corinex Communications Specializes in developing high speed IP communications systems that run over electrical wiring (Powerline), coaxial cables, or phonelines, communications over AnyWireTM. Corinex has 8 years of experience developing and deploying networking products and services for the largest Telecom, Utility, and System Integration companies in the world, including over 50 Utility and 40 Telecom deployments on 6 continents. Corinex customers are leveraging their industry leading product and service expertise to create 200Mbps Triple Play Access Networks, Smart Utility Grids, In-Building networks, and In-Home networks. Contact Corinex today if you are looking to build fast, secure, scalable, cost effective networks that help your company execute on your strategies for innovation and growth.
